diff --git a/changelog/fix_an_invalid_autocorrect_for_rails_strong_parameters_expect_with_dynamic_permit_argument.md b/changelog/fix_an_invalid_autocorrect_for_rails_strong_parameters_expect_with_dynamic_permit_argument.md
